\id JOB Matupi Chin Standard Bible (MCSB)
\h JOBA
\toc1 JOBA
\toc2 Joba
\toc3 Job
\mt1 JOBA
\mt4 (The Book of Job)
\is1 Job Cabu Kawng
\im Job cabu dongah he hlanghing kah patangnah kawng he a thui. Patangnah he tholhnah lamloh ha thoeng tih tholhnah phu ni Pathen loh hlang a patang sak. Cabu dongah he khat neh oldawtnah, hlatnah boeih te hlohlailung la a tael. Olkhueh Rhuem dongah tah Job cabu he olcueih ol la om. Job kah cil te a thui, anih hlang then la om tih Pathen a hinyahnah, boethae saii ham ngaih pawh. Te dae anih te a pumdongah puencakanh, patangnah neh a noemcai. Pathen kah tiktamnah te a dawt tih a laitloeknah khaw a coel, patang a bawtnah ham a bih. Job kah a hui rhoek long khaw amamih kah hmuhnah neh puet a thui uh van. Boeipa loh a thui taktak vaengah tah Pathen kah kopoekrhai neh a longpuei he hlang kah yakmingnah voelah ni a om, patangnah khuiah khaw Pathen thum tite a ming. Job he Boeipa kah yoethennah thai a dang tih camoe thai muep a cun, a khueh tawn khaw a pueh la yet. Joba cabu he 400\sc b.c\sc* tluk vaengah tael coini.
\iot Sawt Yoeinah
